Company Overview of Taconic Capital Advisors L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Taconic Capital Advisors L.P. is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm launches and manages hedge funds. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. The firm employs event-driven, multi-strategy investment approach. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. Taconic Capital Advisors L.P. was founded in 1999 and is based in New York City with additional offices in London, United Kingdom, and Hong Kong.


