                                    Prior                


Prudential Corp. Asia Ltd.


                  Prudential Corp. Asia Ltd., a subsidiary of Prudential Plc, is a Hongkongese company. The firm provides life insurance and fund management operations across Asia. It was founded by Mark Edward Tucker. Nicolaos Andreas Nicandrou is currently the CEO of the firm.                




